org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters

Class AccessSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.AccessSpec

  • public class AccessSpec
extends TLVParameter
    This parameter carries information of the Reader access operation. See also LLRP Specification Section 11.2.1 and LLRP Specification Section 16.2.5.1 .
